$VER: sERiOUS! cDiNFO gUiDE 1.32 (18.9.95)

@node "Introducing" "Introducing"

   This is just another little Tool to make your BBS more comfortable for
   the users.

   It shows you an ANSI and the name and description of the CD that you have
   in any direct exchange subboard or in any device.
@endnode
@node "What`s New ?" "What`s New ?"

   Well I fixed a bug, i forgot to close one file, and so it wasn`t deletable.

   Made the Code just a bit smaller (but not faster ! can anybody send me a
   good Freeware AREXX compiler ?!?)

   There was a bug if you hadn`t typed the devicename exactly as it was..
   so if it was "CD0:" and you typed in "cd0:" nothing happend ;), sorry 
@endnode
@node "Legal Stuff" "Legal Stuff"

   This AREXX Script is FREEWARE! Please do not change the code or remove
